pull_request.title: Tweak Saber params so we can easily implement dagger based on this
pull_request.body: Adds a version of saber with tweaked params. While this is not the full "dagger" implementation we need for PQ wireguard, this will enable us to implement that against the existing interface rather than having to shoehorn the reference dagger implementation into the PQclean code.
